  "title": "Logistics Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE O/N level or ITE</li>\n  <li>Some physical work is required (receiving and issuing components, cycle-counting, etc)</li>\n  <li>Computer literate</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1 year experience in documentation work, which involves generating packslips, invoices, liaising with forwarders or couriers, etc.</li>\n  <li>Follow-up with handling agents for export documents such as export permit, bill of lading, Airwaybill, etc.</li>\n  <li>Able to commence work immediately is preferred</li>\n</ul>",
