    "description": "<p>   EXTRON ELECTRONICS ASIA PTE. LTD.</p>  <p>   Extron Electronics, headquartered in Anaheim, California, has been a leading developer and manufacturer of professional A/V system products. Extron products are used to integrate video and audio into presentation systems for today's high tech boardrooms, presentation/training centers, university lecture halls, and other applications. Our corporate philosophy is founded on three concepts: Service, Support, and Solutions - S3. By following this standard, Extron has become one of the leading providers of products and training to the professional A/V industry. Our customers are our most important asset, and our employees are essential in maintaining that asset.</p>  ",
